---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Moana Live Action Plot - Story & What to Expect (2026)">
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Moana Live Action Plot</h1>
      <p>Everything we know about the story</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="plot-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="plot-card">
        <h2>Official Synopsis</h2>
        <p class="synopsis">In Ancient Polynesia, when a terrible curse incurred by the Demigod Maui reaches Moana's island, she answers the Ocean's call to seek out the Demigod to set things right.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="plot-card">
        <h2>Story Overview</h2>
        <p>Moana live action will follow the same beloved story as the 2016 animated film. The movie follows Moana, the strong-willed daughter of a chief of a Polynesian village, who is chosen by the ocean itself to reunite a mystical relic with the goddess Te Fiti.</p>
        
        <p>When a blight strikes her island, Moana sets sail across the Pacific Ocean to find Maui, a legendary demigod, and save her people. Along the way, they encounter enormous monsters and impossible odds as they complete an action-packed voyage across the open ocean.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="plot-card">
        <h2>Key Story Elements</h2>
        <div class="elements-grid">
          <div class="element">
            <h3>🌊 The Ocean's Chosen One</h3>
            <p>Moana has been chosen by the ocean to restore the heart of Te Fiti, a mystical green stone that holds the power of creation.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="element">
            <h3>💪 The Demigod Maui</h3>
            <p>Maui, a shape-shifting demigod with a magical fishhook, stole the heart of Te Fiti thousands of years ago, causing darkness to spread across the ocean.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="element">
            <h3>🏝️ Saving Motunui</h3>
            <p>Moana's island home is dying because of the curse. She must find Maui and make him return the heart to save her people.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="element">
            <h3>🎵 The Power of Wayfinding</h3>
            <p>Moana rediscovers her ancestors' legacy as master wayfinders, learning to navigate the open ocean by the stars.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="comparison-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Live Action vs Animated: What's Different?</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">While the live action remake will stay true to the original story, there may be some additions and expansions:</p>
      
      <div class="comparison-grid">
        <div class="comparison-card">
          <h3>Potential Additions</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Extended backstory for Moana's ancestors</li>
            <li>More detailed exploration of Polynesian culture</li>
            <li>Additional scenes with supporting characters</li>
            <li>New songs or musical numbers</li>
            <li>Enhanced visual effects for action sequences</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="comparison-card">
          <h3>What Stays the Same</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>The core adventure story</li>
            <li>Moana and Maui's relationship</li>
            <li>Iconic songs like "How Far I'll Go"</li>
            <li>The heartwarming family moments</li>
            <li>The themes of courage and identity</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="characters-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Key Characters in the Story</h2>
      <div class="characters-grid">
        <div class="character-card">
          <h3>Moana</h3>
          <p>The 16-year-old daughter of Chief Tui who dreams of exploring the ocean. She's chosen by the sea to find Maui and restore the heart of Te Fiti.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="character-card">
          <h3>Maui</h3>
          <p>A legendary demigod with the power to shape-shift. He's responsible for stealing the heart of Te Fiti and must help Moana return it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="character-card">
          <h3>Gramma Tala</h3>
          <p>Moana's grandmother who encourages her to follow her dreams and discover her true identity as a wayfinder.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="character-card">
          <h3>Chief Tui</h3>
          <p>Moana's father and the chief of Motunui. He forbids anyone from sailing beyond the reef, hiding a painful family secret.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="character-card">
          <h3>Te Fiti</h3>
          <p>The mother island and creator of all life. Her heart was stolen by Maui, causing darkness to spread across the ocean.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="character-card">
          <h3>Heihei</h3>
          <p>Moana's incredibly dim-witted rooster companion who accidentally stows away on her voyage.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="seo-content">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What is Moana Live Action About?</h2>
      <p>Moana live action is a faithful adaptation of Disney's 2016 animated film. The story follows a young Polynesian girl named Moana who sets sail on a daring mission to save her people. She must find the demigod Maui and convince him to return the mystical heart of Te Fiti to its rightful place.</p>
      
      <h3>Is Moana Live Action a Sequel?</h3>
      <p>No, Moana live action is <strong>not a sequel</strong>. It's a live action remake of the original 2016 animated film, retelling the same story with real actors and enhanced visual effects. Think of it as the same movie brought to life in a new format.</p>
      
      <h3>How Long is Moana Live Action?</h3>
      <p>While the exact runtime hasn't been officially confirmed, the original animated film was 1 hour and 47 minutes. The live action version is expected to have a similar or slightly longer runtime, possibly around <strong>2 hours</strong> to allow for more detailed storytelling and expanded scenes.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0077be 0%, #00d4aa 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .page-header p {
    opacity: 0.9;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  
  .plot-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }
  
  .plot-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }
  
  .plot-card h2 {
    color: var(--dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .synopsis {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    font-style: italic;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: var(--light);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  
  .plot-card p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  
  .elements-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .element {
    background: var(--light);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  
  .element h3 {
    color: var(--dark);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  
  .element p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  
  .comparison-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: var(--light);
  }
  
  .comparison-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--dark);
  }
  
  .section-intro {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .comparison-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .comparison-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }
  
  .comparison-card h3 {
    color: var(--dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .comparison-card ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .comparison-card li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }
  
  .characters-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }
  
  .characters-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--dark);
  }
  
  .characters-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .character-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
  }
  
  .character-card h3 {
    color: var(--dark);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .character-card p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  
  .seo-content {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: white;
  }
  
  .seo-content .container {
    max-width: 800px;
  }
  
  .seo-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--dark);
  }
  
  .seo-content h3 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--dark);
  }
  
  .seo-content p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
